data.text:
Better known as Laurie.

Late of Warrana Village Taree and Wingham Court. Passed away suddenly on Sunday 6th January 2019.

Aged 95 years

Loving husband of Hazel (Dec). Dad to Kevin and Janice. Grandfather to Mathew, Gayle, Anthony, Simon, Vanessa and eleven great grandchildren.
